"
HiRISE has the most beautiful images of Mars available. So what’s the 
copyright restriction? There’s only good news: there is no copyright 
restriction.

All of the images produced by HiRISE and accessible on this site are 
within the public domain: there are no restrictions on their usage by 
anyone in the public, including news or science organizations.

We do ask for a credit line where possible:
   Image: NASA/JPL/University of Arizona

"

